    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this tradition at 3rd level, you gain proficiency in the Insight and Medicine skills, and you gain proficiency with the herbalism kit.</p>\n<p>You also gain a special mask, which you often wear when using the features of this subclass. You determine its appearance, or generate it randomly by rolling on the Merciful Mask table.</p>\n<h3>Merciful Mask</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">d6</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Mask Appearance</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Raven</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Blank and white</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Crying visage</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">4</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Laughing visage</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">5</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Skull</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">6</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Butterfly</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
